- cs.CC (Computational Complexity): This sub-category covers research on the complexity of computational problems and the resources required to solve them. The paper's analysis of the time complexity of the algorithm makes it a possible fit for this sub-category. 
- cs.CG (Computational Geometry): This sub-category covers research on algorithms and data structures for geometric problems. The paper's focus on triangle finding in graphs makes it a possible fit for this sub-category.
